As a subproject only the library is consumed. The tools (xmllint,
xmlcatalog), the test programs and the examples add ~58 compile+link
jobs (~110s CPU) at the tail of the parent build for artifacts nothing
uses.

---
--- a/meson.build
+++ b/meson.build
@@ -474,6 +474,10 @@
 
 meson.override_dependency('libxml-2.0', xml_dep)
 
+# As a subproject only the library is wanted — skip the tools, test
+# programs and examples.
+if not meson.is_subproject()
+
 ## xmllint tool
 
 xmllint = executable(
@@ -566,6 +570,8 @@
 
 subdir('example')
 
+endif
+
 if want_docs or want_python
     subdir('doc')
 endif
